gnetic field), it provides the best prediction among the available models.\nFinally, we compare the star formation and gas properties of this high-redshift\ngalaxy to local star-forming regions and find that the SFK relation provides\nthe best estimates of SFR in both local and high-redshift galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Dec 2017 07:14:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Dec 2017 04:49:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 18 Dec 2017 05:45:49 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 5 Apr 2018 22:51:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-10"}
